# Review Process Rules [CRITICAL]
---
description: Rules governing review processes for user stories
globs: ["**/*review*/**", "**/*.feature", "**/reviews/**", "**/*review*.php", "**/*review*.sh", "**/*US-*/**/reviews/**"]
